entity.description: Dan Le Batard, Stugotz and the Shipping Container offer their unique blend of self-deprecating humor, insightful guests and thought-provoking conversation around the major sports topics of the day. Joined regularly by show friends Greg Cote, Ron Magill, Mina Kimes and countless others, the show weaves between sports and the ridiculous, all in a way to make you laugh and make you think. As Le Batard says, "We are a marching band to nowhere and we look forward to making fun of the powerful, the cliché and ourselves."

entity.description: Veteran Miami Herald columnist and radio host Dan Le Batard leads a humorous, critical and sometimes controversial discussion of the hot sports topics of the day, from the Clevelander Hotel in Miami Beach. He's joined on each 30-minute episode by his father, Gonzalo "Papi" Le Batard.
